{"tid":1946162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 點打大佬好","createTime":"2020-03-27T12:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T14:15:00.000Z","uid":122767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4fdefda301ba8a5e03be55d70c634a43a867b59f","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n譚德塞辭職既聯署緊係要簽啦<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟我地要點打大佬呢<br />\n<br />\n我地要聯署 請求美國/國際組織去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">調查</span></span>譚德塞失職同我地偉大既中國有無關係 <br />\n<br />\n萬一咁唔好彩真係有一啲枱底交易調查到出嚟既話<br />\n<br />\n我地就比左啲<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">子彈</span></span>我地敵人既敵人！<br />\n<br />\n我地要我地既敵人成為全球公敵！<br />\n<br />\n比全球追擊！比全世界追究！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他招！請出招！"},{"pid":"caafa3df4a77604fbcf601e1badfc13afdef008b","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9deec7b9482bb73adc577d48c4249fbaa0de3fff","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92c76009a814949799100cc3aba2bdbf026ae25e","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"287199105eb7ee945d7cd3cd1ba5fe58c288a29b","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38fe2c67f04ae436e74c9e4a6ae6b3e8c7cf5d51","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba6d7d8d63fa65687ed16d95f51fc0d60fee127f","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"825d77b63c024ba570eb4ea909d0aceb84c3841c","tid":1946162,"uid":122767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd3df175a1400fb94